# Nexus environment authority
#
# Application settings for local development are documented in:
#   backend/.env.example
#
# Production-controlled deployment settings are documented in:
#   deploy/.env.controlled.example
#   deploy/.env.controlled.local-postgres.example
#
# Do not duplicate runtime variables in this repository root file. Every
# executable environment variable must have one Settings or deployment owner,
# one documented default and one machine-verified consumer.
